<li id="cite_note-Raymo.2C_Ruddiman-15">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Raymo.2C_Ruddiman_15-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Raymo.2C_Ruddiman_15-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> Raymo, M.E., W.F. Ruddiman, and P.N. Froelich (1988) Influence of late Cenozoic mountain building on ocean geochemical cycles. Geology, v. 16, p. 649-653.</li>
