<td colspan="2" style="width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<table>
<tr>
<th style="background:#408521; width:20%;" colspan="1"><a href="/wiki/Greenhouse_Earth" title="Greenhouse Earth" class="mw-redirect">Greenhouse Earth</a><br />
<p>(global climate where tropical temperatures may reach the poles)</p>
</th>
<th style="background:#B3E2D0; width:60%;" colspan="4"><a href="/wiki/Icehouse_Earth" title="Icehouse Earth" class="mw-redirect">Icehouse Earth</a><br />
<p>(global climate where ice ages are possible)</p>
</th>
<th style="background:#DDFFDD; width:20%;" colspan="1"><a href="/wiki/Snowball_Earth" title="Snowball Earth">Snowball Earth</a><br />
<p>(ice covers whole planet in global ice age)</p>
</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="background:#408521; font-size: 100%; text-align:center; width:20%"><a href="/wiki/Climate" title="Climate">Climate</a> similar to <a href="/wiki/Interstadial" title="Interstadial" class="mw-redirect">Interstadials</a></td>
<td style="background:#B3E2D0; font-size: 100%; text-align:center; width:15%"><a href="/wiki/Interglacial" title="Interglacial">Interglacial</a> (longer warm period during ice age, such as today)</td>
<td style="background:#B3E2D0; font-size: 100%; text-align:center; width:15%"><a href="/wiki/Interstadial" title="Interstadial" class="mw-redirect">Interstadial</a> (brief warm period during ice age, weaker than interglacial)</td>
<td style="background:#B3E2D0; font-size: 100%; text-align:center; width:15%"><a href="/wiki/Stadial" title="Stadial">stadial</a> (brief cooler period during interglacial, such as <a href="/wiki/Older_Dryas" title="Older Dryas">Older Dryas</a>, <a href="/wiki/Younger_Dryas" title="Younger Dryas">Younger Dryas</a>, <a href="/wiki/Little_Ice_Age" title="Little Ice Age">Little Ice Age</a>)</td>
<td style="background:#B3E2D0; font-size: 100%; text-align:center; width:15%"><a href="/wiki/Ice_Age" title="Ice Age" class="mw-redirect">Ice Age</a>/Glacial (expansion of <a href="/wiki/Ice_cap" title="Ice cap">ice caps</a>)</td>
<td style="background:#DDFFDD; font-size: 100%; text-align:center; width:20%">global ice age</td>
</tr>
